<br>
The problem with the Hole for a group of sub-60's would be the rock golems.  The problem with KC and ghetto AE is that you run a high risk of training other people and getting warnings.  In fact, one time Meto, Jangos and I were running around Karnors pulling trains of 10-15 and beating them yet the people in the zone soon called the GM's on to us because we were &quot;training&quot;, even though one man's train is another man's pull.<br>
<br>
I hate to say it, but I also think Ghetto AE is one of the few times where having *uber gear* (yes i hate that phrase) actually makes a noticeable difference.  When we're doing Ghetto AE, my AC is usually around 1550+.  There are times when the entire group, even in all this *uber gear* gets down to 1 bubble of health.  Obviously in this situation the extra HP and AC on gear are the saving grace.<br>
<br>
Anyway, ghetto AE rules.  It's tons of fun.  And I *think* a sub 60 group could do it if everyone had mad skills.  Just be ready to die. . .after all, what fun is it if you're not coming close to dying?  If you're worried about death and exp loss, you're better off pulling singles to the zone line. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#212141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uaelodyn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aelodyn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/MojoRisenn/grouchy.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 42<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/14/02 1:59:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub114.ezboard.com/flegacyofsteel43089general.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2953.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ring on Front Page</span><hr size=1> I had a feeling ghetto AE was a combination of level 60, skill, and mad gear. I'm thinking your average level 60 group would get pasted.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ucervantus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cervantus</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://cervant.netfirms.com/yy.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 42<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/14/02 2:04:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub114.ezboard.com/flegacyofsteel43089general.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2953.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ring on Front Page</span><hr size=1> are you using AoE proc weapons in the ghetto ae groups? <p>You should hate me with a passion, or love me to death</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#212141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uyvin.