<br>
2) Shamans:  Tigirs tugurs and torpor, if they have the mana shoot a few of the poison rains<br>
<br>
3) rogues monks paladins warriors SK's, pull stuff off of the cleric, if you can equip an AE proc weapon use it.<br>
<br>
4) Rangers: as above with rest of melee, but add damage sheilds<br>
<br>
5) druids:  damage sheilds, spot heals, and if your feeling couragous  an AE nuke or two <br>
<br>
6) clerics: keep us alive, dot heals early on are best, and try to stay out of the mess<br>
<br>
7) pure casters:  havent really though of a use yet, cant take the beating.<br>
<br>
<br>
the cool thing about it is once you have a bard and a shaman, you have your ghetto AE group.<br>
